headline: Jacobs Awarded Contract to Modernize One of the Largest Advanced Wastewater Treatment Facilities in Western US
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected as the progressive design-build contractor for upgrades to the San José–Santa Clara Regional Wastewater Facility (RWF) in California. This $200 million project will modernize the city's biosolids treatment infrastructure, delivering long-term reliability at the second largest advanced wastewater treatment plant in the western United States.
